{"tid":698834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國移回南海飛彈系統","createTime":"2018-06-12T05:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T10:06:37.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4431870d87e8f46bae656d4797f0e02bc7339f4a","tid":698834,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:01:28.000Z","msg":"中國移回南海飛彈系統<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018-06-12<br />\n<br />\n正值美國與中國在南海激烈角力的敏感時刻，以色列情報分析公司「國際衛星影像公司」十一日指出，中國部署在南海西沙群島永興島上的飛彈系統，三日才顯示有部分設施不見蹤影，八日拍攝的最新空拍照卻再次出現被撤離的飛彈系統。分析指出，中國此前撤離飛彈，可能是為了緩解與美國之間的緊張情勢。也有專家指出，中國可能是因飛彈系統不適合當地環境，或受到鹹水損傷，暫時性移除部份設備進行修繕、替換。（編譯劉宜庭）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1208245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1208245&d=2lwlGKa7mSP44RAh4nKyUtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b5efe20e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1208245&h=713ac450\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1208245</a>"},{"pid":"645384be8ed5ccbf7db15dbadbcf2aba0f3684b7","tid":698834,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:02:16.000Z","msg":"受到鹹水損傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed64e2f04156d6f64a88efc01b845d42dd7d9d2","tid":698834,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"645384be8ed5ccbf7db15dbadbcf2aba0f3684b7","tid":698834,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:02:16.000Z","msg":"受到鹹水損傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"擺幾日又換一批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg